}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== WET11 v2 serial numbers appear to start with '''BBQ1'''.
"WET11V2 REV:XA" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. This is assumed to be a BroMax device.
[http://shacktopus.com/hacks/senao-wet11.html Internal photo of the v2] :"3752-13050011" is silkscreened on the boad.
